{"tid":1625900,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我宣布今晚有咩打爛商舖搶嘢嘅 一律都係黑警做","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:23:09.000Z","uid":51790,"like":58,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"da34cb108fedddefd24afa5bccf23e2488299acd","tid":1625900,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"收到風(from 政府AO朋友) 今日黑警會出嚟扮示威者<br />\n爆舖加搶嘢<br />\n目標好可能係銀行金舖<br />\n啲狗唔會阻止 由得啲人搶<br />\n誤導外國傳媒等全世界都以為香港人示威已經變質<br />\n跟住大條道理行更嚴苛法例<br />\n<br />\n所以已經通知啲連鎖舖今日要早收<br />\n七仔都收埋皮就係咁解<br />\n手足冷靜啲 唔好急於一時<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母黑警<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f17077fbdfd16992c6085e1e5448ae250f0734","tid":1625900,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"星期日 1400 港島九龍自己揀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625896</a><br />\n<br />\n一齊討論下？"},{"pid":"6a5a6cac1a662be4f414ee0a0c07a09fc7d5a461","tid":1625900,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3589dad32ed4d05dd804fd1e94976894b7003f7","tid":1625900,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"5dfc48a22af330e7bf68168e9da1c156dfefb9c6","tid":1625900,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff554b0b89fdde2b63f2c64dd187f453c303893","tid":1625900,"uid":301479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da34cb108fedddefd24afa5bccf23e2488299acd","tid":1625900,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"收到風(from 政府AO朋友) 今日黑警會出嚟扮示威者<br />\n爆舖加搶嘢<br />\n目標好可能係銀行金舖<br />\n啲狗唔會阻止 由得啲人搶<br />\n誤導外國傳媒等全世界都以為香港人示威已經變質<br />\n跟住大條道理行更嚴苛法例<br />\n<br />\n所以已經通知啲連鎖舖今日要早收<br />\n七仔都收埋皮就係咁解<br />\n手足冷靜啲 唔好急於一時<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母黑警<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"明明琴晚十八區咁大成效，結果今日一立完法就吹風全民休息，要休息嘅自已休飽佢，今晩八點，唔想休息嘅，老地方！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間：8 pm 集合<br />\n<br />\n地點：第一集合點／第二集合點／第三集合點<br />\n<br />\n深水埗：南昌V walk／楓樹街遊樂場／長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n荃灣：沙咀道遊樂場／荃灣公園<br />\n葵芳：葵廣／林士德足球場／林金殿外<br />\n青衣：青衣城<br />\n觀塘：apm／觀塘遊樂場<br />\n九龍塘：又一城<br />\n九龍灣：德福<br />\n黃大仙：黃大仙中心／黃大仙廣場／摩士公園<br />\n油尖旺：朗豪坊／麥花臣球場<br />\n紅土黃何九：馬頭圍邨球場／亞皆老街球場<br />